OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FMr John confirmed he would be stepping
OL,7,Fdown with immediate effect in a
OL,8,Fstatement issued on Friday evening,
OL,9,Fwhile he will also retire as Bishop of
OL,10,FBangor on August 31. There is no
OL,11,Fsuggestion the archbishop behaved
OL,12,Finappropriately.
OL,14,FThe Church in Wales' representative
OL,15,Fbody is calling for "change in
OL,16,Fleadership, procedures and governance
OL,17,Fin the Diocese of Bangor".
