OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FThe Archbishop's announcement followed
OL,7,Fa safeguarding review at Bangor
OL,8,FCathedral which identified "a culture
OL,9,Fin which sexual boundaries seemed
OL,10,Fblurred" and "promiscuity was
OL,11,Facceptable".
OL,13,FMr John commissioned two reports into
OL,14,Fthe North Wales cathedral in October
OL,15,Flast year.
