OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FA summary of a report shared on the
OL,7,FChurch in Wales' website said there
OL,8,Fwere also reports of "inappropriate
OL,9,Flanguage, rude jokes and innuendoes in
OL,10,Fthe choir that left some feeling
OL,11,Funsafe and marginalised".
OL,13,FInappropriate language was also used
OL,14,Fin front of younger members of the
OL,15,Fchoir and at times caused "humiliation
OL,16,Fto some", the report's compilers were
OL,17,Ftold.
