OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FOther issues raised included the
OL,7,Fpresence of hurtful gossip, a poor
OL,8,Fsafeguarding approach and weak
OL,9,Ffinancial controls.
OL,11,FNow, the representative body of the
OL,12,FChurch in Wales said it will
OL,13,Fcommission a safeguarding audit of all
OL,14,Fcathedrals in Wales "to assure itself
OL,15,Fthat appropriate procedures and
OL,16,Fprotocols relating to safeguarding are
OL,17,Fbeing followed diligently", as well as
OL,18,Fa cultural audit of the Church in
OL,19,FWales.
