OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FIn a statement, the representative
OL,7,Fbody said: "The trustees of the
OL,8,Frepresentative body of the Church in
OL,9,FWales acknowledge with deep concern
OL,10,Fthe serious issues raised in recent
OL,11,Freports and correspondence regarding
OL,12,Fleadership, safeguarding, management,
OL,13,Fand conduct in the central structures
OL,14,Fof Bangor Diocese and at Bangor
OL,15,FCathedral.
OL,26,@oD@LOU
