OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,F"As the charitable trustee body
OL,7,Fresponsible for stewarding assets and
OL,8,Fdistributing funding to both the
OL,9,Fdiocese and the cathedral, we take our
OL,10,Fduty of care and accountability to the
OL,11,FChurch and wider community with the
OL,12,Futmost seriousness."
OL,14,F"The revelations of safeguarding
OL,15,Ffailures, blurred boundaries,
OL,16,Finappropriate conduct, weak control
OL,17,Fenvironment and lack of transparency
OL,18,Fin management at Bangor Cathedral are
OL,19,Fdeeply troubling."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@RO]
