OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FOther recommendations from the
OL,7,Frepresentative body include the
OL,8,FCathedral Chapter launching an
OL,9,Fexternal investigation "into the
OL,10,Fbehaviour, culture and activities of
OL,11,Fthe Cathedral Choir and due attention
OL,12,Fis given to the issues identified in
OL,13,Fthe reports relating to the choir", as
OL,14,Fwell as an independent financial audit
OL,15,Ftaking place.
