OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,FThe statement added: "The
OL,7,Frepresentative body will continue to
OL,8,Fmonitor the situation closely and
OL,9,Freserves the right to review and, if
OL,10,Fnecessary, adjust funding arrangements
OL,11,Fin accordance with our due diligence
OL,12,Fresponsibilities as trustees.
OL,14,F"We urge the Diocese and Cathedral to
OL,15,Fact swiftly and transparently to
OL,16,Frestore trust and ensure a safe,
OL,17,Faccountable environment for all."
OL,26,@nD@VOU
