OL,3,CChurch in Wales calls for cultural
OL,4,Creview and safeguarding audit
OL,6,F"We remain committed to supporting the
OL,7,Fmission and ministry of the Church in
OL,8,FWales in Bangor and across Wales,
OL,9,Falways guided by our duty to protect
OL,10,Fthe vulnerable and steward our
OL,11,Fresources for the common good of the
OL,12,FChurch in Wales."
OL,14,FAnnouncing his retirement, Mr John
OL,15,Fsaid: "It has been an enormous joy to
OL,16,Fserve in the Church in Wales for over
OL,17,F35 years.
OL,19,F"I would very much like to thank the
OL,20,Fclergy and congregations of this
OL,21,Fwonderful diocese before I retire."
