OL,6,FAfter the publication of a summary
OL,7,Finto the reports earlier this year,
OL,8,Fthe archbishop said: "I acknowledge
OL,9,Fthat these findings are hard to hear `
OL,10,Fbut they must be faced if we are to
OL,11,Fmove forward with integrity."
OL,13,F"I have begun reflecting on what I
OL,14,Fmust learn from this process ` not
OL,15,Fonly as a leader, but as a fellow
OL,16,Fpilgrim," he added.
OL,26,@pD@VOUsD@]O]uD@AOUxD@IO]
