OL,6,F"While this has been a sobering time,
OL,7,Fit also offers us opportunity for
OL,8,Fchange. It will mean hard work, but it
OL,9,Fcan also bring healing, and we do not
OL,10,Fdo this alone."
OL,12,FMr John became Bishop of Bangor in
OL,13,F2008 and was elected Archbishop of
OL,14,FWales in December 2021.
